<doc id="738455" wikidata="Q606414" url="?curid=738455" title="Inge II">
<text>Inge II may refer to:

*Inge II of Sweden, Ingold Halstensson, also called Inge the Younger, king of Sweden in 1110–1125
*Inge II of Norway, Inge Baardson (1185–1217)</text><links>
<link wikidata="Q471475" start="24" end="41" title="Inge II of Sweden" label="Inge II of Sweden"/>
<link wikidata="Q365035" start="122" end="139" title="Inge II of Norway" label="Inge II of Norway"/>
</links>
