==Twin towns – sister cities==

Joniškis is twinned with:
* Auce, Latvia
* Dobele, Latvia
* Jelgava Municipality, Latvia
* Konin, Poland
* Novoselitsky District, Russia
* Sulingen, Germany
* Ungheni, Moldova
* Vimmerby, Sweden
* Võru, Estonia
