* &quot;Consolida regalis&quot; (syn. &quot;Delphinium consolida&quot;) — field larkspur: Western Asia, Europe
** &quot;C. r.&quot; subsp. &quot;divaricata&quot; (syn. &quot;Consolida divaricata&quot;)
